{"tid":1786773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【保良局主席】馬清楠唔想太多人探望局童 怕太多禮物寵壞小朋友","createTime":"2019-12-17T11:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T15:18:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aedfda8b9d3a54cacec1bb7bf7bca7ea4e1003e9","tid":1786773,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:28:30.000Z","msg":"保良局主席馬清楠在任9個月，還有3個月便卸任，他笑言不會不捨得，只感到開心又辛苦，並希望他帶頭的工作會繼續下去，他說：「我哋行政費係咁多慈善團體中最低，係最慳家嘅，我哋服務對象有70萬人，希望可以繼續關懷多方面有需要嘅人。」他又指自己推行多運動，而自己亦身體力行，與同事行山，又會跟兒子打壁球，每天運動超過1小時。<br />\n今天馬清楠在銅鑼灣出席支票遞交儀式，由品牌捐出逾13萬元，馬清楠指品牌很有愛心，除了製作teddy bear作慈善義賣，更送了300隻給局童，馬清楠說：「我哋好多小朋友嚟自複雜家庭，佢哋喺呢度好開心，有個溫暖嘅家，不過都唔想太多人嚟探望，因為好多人嚟到都送禮物，唔想寵壞佢哋。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191217/large/1576577130_4a7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576577130_4a7d.jpg&h=26d3f0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191217/60388367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F60388367&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0sRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=66a917bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F60388367&h=a299b05d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191217/60388367</a>"},{"pid":"2029385734c3ab193e639f035e1cf8300b38a0d9","tid":1786773,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 - 支援手足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786710</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"990070d30dc591e1aef97adcff6ec885ae1c2023","tid":1786773,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAN9QVS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAN9QVS.jpg&h=daf7e9c7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}